title: Tremont -- 2446 W. 10th Street
posting_body: ['Tremont House for Rent', 'Updated 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath in the upscale Tremont Area of Cleveland.', 'The unit is the entire first floor of the beautiful Victorian double house located at 2446 W. 10th Street.', 'The house includes all appliances (stove, refrigerator, washer and dryer).', 'This home is updated, including whole house air conditioning, and well insulated for lower utility bills.', ' Security cameras for your comfort and safety.', 'The small second bedroom would make a perfect home office or study for a professional.', 'This spacious unit affords you the privacy and comfort of living in the middle of exciting city life.', 'Appropriate pets considered with a pet privilege fee.', 'This house will not be available long.', 'CALL MIKE TO SET AN APPOINTMENT TO SEE!', '440 - Five  Eight Two – 36 Zero 6.', 'Tremont is located on the near West Side of Cleveland with easy access to all city attractions.', 'The area is noted for its strong community festivities, famous restaurants, wine and art walks, art in the park, and art galleries throughout the area.', 'All this for only $1500.00 per month.', 'One year lease, Security Deposit and Credit / Background check required.']
